7. Routing Fundamentals

Supported routing protocols:

Static Routing

OSPF

IS-IS

BGP

RIP

Example (Static Route):

set routing-options static route 0.0.0.0/0 next-hop 192.168.1.254

8. Security Basics (SRX)

Key concepts:

Zones (trust, untrust)

Policies

NAT

Stateful firewall

Traffic flows are controlled by security policies, not interfaces alone.

